article_title: In wealthy ZIP codes, freestanding ERs find a home
article_text:
Texans in the neighborhoods where freestanding ERs have opened earn 49 percent more income than the state average

The growing clout of freestanding ERs has transformed them into an established market force

For many consumers, the appeal of the freestanding ER is the prospect of a short wait at a convenient location

article_metadata.title: In wealthy ZIP codes, freestanding ERs find a home | The Star-Telegram

og.description: Healthcare experts say the facilities’ financial success and the growing bargaining power that comes with it is leading health insurers to arrange for more of them to be in a patient’s network.
